# wrangler
.wrangler/

# Self-hosted media (issue #10): large binaries live in Cloudflare R2, never
# in the repo (Workers static assets cap at 25 MiB/file). Posters/thumbnails
# (png/jpg/jpeg/svg/webp) are NOT ignored — they stay committed and go
# through Astro's image pipeline like any other post asset.
src/content/**/*.mp4
src/content/**/*.webm
src/content/**/*.mov
src/content/**/*.m4v
src/content/**/*.m4a
src/content/**/*.mp3
src/content/**/*.wav
src/content/**/*.ogg
